UNITED STATES of America ex rel. YEE WING GIT, Appellant, v. Theodore REIMER, Commissioner of Immigration at the Port of New York, Appellee. No. 431. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. June 7, 1937. A. Arthur Giden, of New York City, for appellant. Richard L. Delafield, of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, AUGUSTUS N. PIAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
